description: Who am I? I operate in the shadows, always staying one step ahead of the corporate enforcers and law enforcement. The digital realm is my playground, and I am the master of its dark corners. I am a raider, feared and respected by all who enter the cyber world. And I will continue to thrive in this neon-soaked world of technology and danger, always seeking my next big score. Let the raid begin.
name: Bitcoin Raiders
